(14, 'EGO LITE', '2024-10-06 14:45:10', '2024-10-06 14:45:10', 'ego-assets/images/product_categories/1728204310_Ego Lite PNG.png', '<p>Ego Lite is a premium brand under Ego Vision, offering high-quality soft contact lenses designed for comfort and clarity. These lenses provide an exceptional visual experience, making them a preferred choice for customers seeking both style and performance.</p>'),
